code: import{createAsyncThunk,createSlice}from'@reduxjs/toolkit';import axios from'axios';var initialState={BusinessRecent:[],loading:false,error:''};export var fetchData=createAsyncThunk('businessRecent/fetchData',function(){return axios.get('data/BusinessMostRecent.json').then(function(res){return res.data;});});var BusinessRecentSlice=createSlice({name:'businessRecent',initialState:initialState,extraReducers:function extraReducers(builder){builder.addCase(fetchData.pending,function(state){state.loading=true;});builder.addCase(fetchData.fulfilled,function(state,action){state.loading=false;state.error='';state.BusinessRecent=action.payload;});builder.addCase(fetchData.rejected,function(state,action){state.loading=false;state.BusinessRecent=[];state.error=action.error.message;});}});export default BusinessRecentSlice.reducer;
